data.description: Charming furnished single-family home in the Mainlands of Tamarac community! Move-in-ready, featuring a one-car garage, tiled flooring throughout, with the added benefits of AC and roof installed approximately 5 years ago. Relaxing screen patio overlooking the backyard with a banana tree. Notable upgrades include replaced sewer and pipes, a significant investment of about 20K, ensuring long-term durability.
